{"tid":2083070,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"RTHK: 中國派武術教練駐青藏高原　分析指中印邊境衝突有關","createTime":"2020-06-28T13:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T14:47:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0cbfeef7f2b2b040c0b8b19c44c4e3742f0ad8","tid":2083070,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:26:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534533-20200628.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534533-20200628.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8WVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=015a3d44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534533-20200628.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3d59f235\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534533-20200628.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中國派遣20名武術教練到青藏高原，訓練武裝部隊人員。北京方面無解釋今次部署的原因，外界估計可能與早前中印邊境軍人，爆發流血衝突有關。<br />\n<br />\n央視早前報道，20名來自一個搏擊會的戰鬥員，派駐到西藏首府拉薩。指揮官接受訪問時說，這批戰鬥員會訓練武裝部隊的組織及動員能力，令部隊能更快作出反應及提供支援。報道未有提及這批戰鬥員，會否訓練接壤印度地區的邊防部隊。<br />\n<br />\n中印邊防士兵於本月15日，在加勒萬河谷爆發衝突，最少20名印度軍人死亡，中國暫未公布死傷數字。美國一間衛星影像公司發放的最新圖片顯示，中印雙方在事發後，都加強邊境建築活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iVWs-c8oBiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiVWs-c8oBiU&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8WVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=8fd5a087\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iVWs-c8oBiU</a>"},{"pid":"b431876b32ba13ee8f964addf7b75f8c9a48170e","tid":2083070,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3767041/org/bfe7c92e8286ea7a6869609b725b1947.jpg/sVHe5gWtCXqHUTSRYML2VoNPsPt3ff-71tpqzNbaasw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3767041%2Forg%2Fbfe7c92e8286ea7a6869609b725b1947.jpg%2FsVHe5gWtCXqHUTSRYML2VoNPsPt3ff-71tpqzNbaasw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6f611bdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"596ca12d26ab3e963ebb2ddf902905653be18326","tid":2083070,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"中國人睇《葉問》睇到HIGH到一個點<br />\n<br />\n以為係可以去真打！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3767041%2Forg%2Fbfe7c92e8286ea7a6869609b725b1947.jpg%2FsVHe5gWtCXqHUTSRYML2VoNPsPt3ff-71tpqzNbaasw%3Fv%3Dw1920&amp;h=6f611bdb&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"a8a02a4ed6a2d8777f5a83fcf21ecd6ef1687a31","tid":2083070,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:29:16.000Z","msg":"重現616宣傳攻勢，將自己所有FACEBOOK，IG，Twitter，Google頭像換成71文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2083027/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2083027/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0GN9Rk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0GN9Rk.jpg&h=f0ca8213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"856626d2edc1258eda73284d86b1a2c8d03c4e5c","tid":2083070,"uid":288765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"笑林功夫加足球？？？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373b779dccec60d0125d1f403a878c5a204ad13b","tid":2083070,"uid":222448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"義和拳 2.0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067b8e78cc15225ac10187f4260f2837e62aa061","tid":2083070,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:50:34.000Z","msg":"可以擋子彈？"},{"pid":"ff067dc01941d468fe3732ff09389b0c68b6ad6d","tid":2083070,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"雷雷大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710bd6db169b5ee9040942695f9ae43cd8aeb2e4","tid":2083070,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vcqvomM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvcqvomM.gif&h=0bd8c0ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83ae6940fcdd231846db2bfd17d8ce217dba65c6","tid":2083070,"uid":42730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"少林功夫源出印度嚟嘅達摩<br />\n<br />\n印度出返瑜伽大師KO武術指導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7fe793eedfec2461122d2e7219724ec9796a5f","tid":2083070,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:27:53.000Z","msg":"終於發現只有摺被大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1729ce5b3ed0aa21421ef6d63c103a41453a91e1","tid":2083070,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:32:18.000Z","msg":"上到高源班教頭唔知有幾多人有高山症呢？<br />\n剩低嘅有幾多個夠氣打晒一套拳呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20d0d6427140febc6349f9eb4f77c478c96fd5c","tid":2083070,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:33:02.000Z","msg":"想學太極高手比人打到訓嚮度？<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"bc80e2bcf4c28201f43ebb44ac32c8fbf0fa0426","tid":2083070,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"856626d2edc1258eda73284d86b1a2c8d03c4e5c","tid":2083070,"uid":288765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"笑林功夫加足球？？？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"鐵頭功吖喇"},{"pid":"92da2559031ef1f1cde0abd0f99a87893370ad64","tid":2083070,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:36:42.000Z","msg":"太極大師？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b1fe09e1079853d4315329a010c57e24aee107","tid":2083070,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"徐曉東心諗"}]}